headline: 4 Utility Stocks to Bet on From the Thriving Electric Power Industry
summary: Amid rising demand for electricity and an increase in the unit price of electricity, utilities like ED, DTE, CNP and EVRG are set to benefit from strong demand from their stable customer base.
